sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor O as Owner
    participant V as View (NewAd.html)
    participant P as Presenter (Ads.js)
    participant A as API (ads.php)
    participant M as Model (AdModel.php)
    participant DB as MySQL Database
    participant FS as FileSystem (Docker Vol)

    Note over O, V: Scenario: Owner uploads a new room ad

    O->>V: Fills Data + Selects Photo
    O->>V: Clicks "Publish"
    
    V->>P: 'submit' event
    activate P
    
    Note right of P: Uses FormData to handle<br/>text fields and binary files
    P->>P: new FormData(formElement)
    
    P->>A: FETCH POST /api/ads (Multipart/form-data)
    activate A
    
    Note right of A: Checks active session
    A->>A: checkSession()
    
    A->>M: createAd(data, files)
    activate M
    
    %% IMAGE HANDLING BLOCK
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over M, FS: Image Upload Handling
        M->>M: Generate unique filename
        M->>FS: move_uploaded_file(temp, /uploads/img.jpg)
        FS-->>M: Save confirmation
    end
    
    %% DB INSERTION
    M->>DB: INSERT INTO ads (title, price, img_path) VALUES (?, ?, ?)
    activate DB
    DB-->>M: Return New Ad ID
    deactivate DB
    
    M-->>A: Return Success (Ad ID)
    deactivate M
    
    A-->>P: JSON { success: true, id: 101 }
    deactivate A
    
    P->>V: Show message "Ad Published!"
    P->>V: window.location.href = '/my-ads'
    deactivate P

    V->>O: Show message "Ad Published!"
    V->>O: Show personal Ads
